<cb:div type="xuzang-notes">
<head>卍續藏 校勘記</head>
<p>
<note n="0796b03" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0796b03">分攝者言此淨土之教亦攝得上三教然畢竟不同以大小異故全攝者言淨土之教全同上三教也</note>
<note n="0796b04" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0796b04">以下言淨土終不同于純有之教</note>
<note n="0796b05" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0796b05">言十善乃人天二乘菩薩及一切佛法皆因此成就故修淨土者必行十善此所以分攝純有教也</note>
<note n="0797b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0797b01">言諸佛應化之身無量而一一如其所應之佛皆承事之</note>
<note n="0797b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0797b02">決定性謂決定安於小乘不向大乘也</note>
<note n="0797b03" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0797b03">以下言淨土終不同於超寂之教</note>
<note n="0797b04" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0797b04">深信淨土是為正信願生淨土是為正願等字含正行等如稱名觀像觀想寔相乃至發菩提心皆淨土之正行也</note>
<note n="0797b05" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0797b05">一行三昧言上此念佛一事遂得三昧也</note>
<note n="0797b06" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0797b06">十地又為初地初地又為八地正言無階級之分非從一地始至一地者比也</note>
<note n="0798b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0798b01">此通明淨土全是圓極教義</note>
<note n="0798b02" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0798b02">二二句引法華下說本經</note>
<note n="0799b01" resp="#resp2" place="foot text" type="orig_biao" target="#nkr_note_orig_biao_0799b01">慈善根力者以慈悲之善根合得如是力也</note>
</p>
